[thinking] **Considering method reflection**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking that InvokerHelper might need reflection metadata for the method to work properly. There's a chance it could fail if that’s not the case. Since Groovy's dynamic nature often has metadata, but when it comes to native methods, I wonder if that applies. Existing rest-assured really relies on Groovy and its metadata. But maybe we don’t need to add more metadata after all. It might be best if the test runs natively by default.
